www.businessinsider.com%2Fhouthis-getting-smarter-red-sea-attacks-ships-paying-the-price-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrone%20boats%20packed%20with%20explosives%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20strike%20merchant%20vessels.%20These%20vessels%20are%20largely%20defenseless%2C%20unlike%20the%20US%20warships%20in%20the%20area%2C%20which%20so%20far%20haven't%20been%20hit%20despite%20some%20close%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20Tanker%20War%20and%20what%20we%20are%20doing%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20is%20that%20longer%2C%20enduring%20threat%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20be%20inside%20of%20a%20larger%20area%20%E2%80%94%20always%20having%20that%20risk%20of%20being%20targeted%20or%20having%20an%20engagement%20that's%20going%20to%20have%20to%20take%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20challenges%20%E2%80%94%20from%20detection%20and%20the%20sustainment%2C%20and%20the%20watch%20teams%20and%20the%20readiness%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20lot%20higher%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20why%20I%20compare%20that%20more%20so%20to%20World%20War%20II%20than%2C%20I'd%20say%2C%20even%20outpacing%20what%20was%20seen%20during%20the%20Tanker%20War.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229f094dbc-b006-4bbb-82f5-0b0463276f84%5C%22%3EIntense%20air-defense%20battles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EArcher%20Macy%2C%20a%20retired%20Navy%20admiral%20who%20served%20on%20the%20amphibious%20transport%20dock%20USS%20La%20Salle%20during%20the%20Tanker%20War%2C%20emphasized%20the%20high%20level%20of%20readiness%20required%20of%20the%20American%20warships%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22FILE%20-%20This%20Sept.%2021%2C%201987%20file%20photo%20shows%20mines%20aboard%20the%20Iranian%20ship%20Iran%20Ajr%20being%20inspected%20by%20a%20boarding%20party%20from%20the%20USS%20Lasalle%20in%20the%20Persian%20Gulf.%20Mysterious%20attacks%20on%20oil%20tankers%20near%20the%20st