a%20first.%20Also%2C%20I%20want%20to%20sit%20back%20and%20see%20what%20happens%20with%20the%20housing%20market%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20both%20decided%20it%20would%20be%20at%20least%20three%20years%20before%20we%20bought%20another%20house.%20Housing%20prices%20are%20actually%20higher%20in%20our%20new%20state%2C%20Tennessee%20%E2%80%94%20we%20lived%20in%20Illinois%20previously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20while%20we'll%20need%20time%20to%20save%20up%20a%20larger%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-much-down-payment-for-a-house%5C%22%3Edown%20payment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20also%20have%20more%20knowledge%20than%20we%20did%20as%20first-time%20homebuyers.%20Buying%20a%20new%20home%20comes%20with%20so%20many%20expected%20and%20unexpected%20costs%20such%20as%20closing%20costs%2C%20moving%20expenses%2C%20repairs%2C%20furniture%2C%20and%20home%20upgrades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20CD%20money%20will%20come%20in%20handy%20whenever%20we%20do%20buy%20a%20home%20again%20and%20need%20extra%20money%20to%20cover%20various%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20our%20goals%20for%20the%20%2410%2C000%20we%20put%20into%20a%20CD%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20feel%20that%20comfortable%20investing%20the%20money%20instead%20since%20our%20investments%20are%20for%20more%20long-term%20goals.%20Therefore%2C%20they%20can%20withstand%20the%20ups%20and%20downs%20of%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20February%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwait-better-housing-market-sell-house-cd-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721473682000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6001d405e3d62500185fcce0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwait-better-housing-market-sell-house-cd-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20sold%20our%20house%20and%20moved%20to%20a%20new%20state%2C%20but%20we're%20waiting%20to%20buy%20again.%20A%20CD%20is%20a%20great%20way%20to%20grow%20some%20of%20the%20proceeds%20from%20the%20sale%20until%20then.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Chonc%C3%A9%20Maddox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwait-better-housing-market-sell-house-cd-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20was%20US%20Rep%20Sheila%20Jackson%20Lee%20who%20made%20Juneteenth%20a%20federal%20holiday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721473480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111885149%2Cimgsize-155518.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwho-was-us-rep-sheila-jackson-lee-of-texas-remembering-progressive-hero-who-made-juneteenth-a-federal-holiday%2Farticleshow%2F111884951.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Democrat%2C%20Jackson%20Lee%20had%20represented%20her%20Houston-based%20district%20and%20the%20nation's%20fourth-largest%20city%20since%201995.%20Despite%20a%20previous%20battle%20with%20breast%20cancer%2C%20she%20announced%20her%20pancreatic%20cancer%20diagnosis%20on%20June%202%2C%20remaining%20steadfast%20in%20her%20faith%20and%20commitment%20to%20her%20duties.%20Bishop%20James%20Dixon%2C%20a%20longtime%20friend%2C%20described%20her%20as%20a%20relentless%20fighter%20who%20gave%20everything%20she%20had%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20others.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Employers%20can%20tell%20when%20you%20use%20ChatGPT%20in%20your%20job%20applications.%20So%20stop%20copy-pasting%20and%20do%20this%20instead.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222310%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20sitting%20at%20a%20computer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664611db14fb5b23cc5d08a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221298%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMore%20job%20seekers%20are%20using%20AI-generated%20responses%20in%20their%20applications.%3Cp%3EDelmaine%20Donson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJob%20seekers%20using%20AI-generated%20applications%20face%20detection%20and%20potential%20rejection%20by%20employers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECompanies%20note%20an%20uptick%20in%20AI-written%20job%20applications%2C%20complicating%20the%20hiring%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExperts%20suggest%20customizing%20AI%20assistance%20to%20stand%20out%20%E2%80%94%20using%20it%20as%20an%20editor%20instead%20of%20a%20writer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20hoping%20to%20use%20ChatGPT%20to%20get%20a%20leg%20up%20on%20job%20applications%2C%20you%20might%20just%20be%20shooting%20yourself%20in%20the%20foot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Fhow-ai-is-helping-hiring-managers-recruit-smarter-and-faster%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompanies%20have%20been%20leveraging%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20automatically%20weed%20out%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%2C%20job%20seekers%20have%20begun%20responding%20with%20chatbot-generated%20applications%20to%20keep%20up%20%E2%80%94%20and%20employers%20are%20noticing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJakob%20Knutzen%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20video%20collaboration%20platform%20Butter%2C%20said%20he%20received%20around%20450%20applicants%20for%20a%20product%20designer%20position.%20But%20Knutzen%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20was%20able%20to%20detect%20what%20he%20believed%20was%20ample%20usage%20of%20ChatGPT-written%20responses%20to%20the%20form's%20three%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20formulations%20were%20incredibly%20similar%20and%20used%20a%20bunch%20of%20phrases%20that%20I%20would%20never%20imagine%20people%20using%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Knutzen%20took%20his%20concerns%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fjakobknutzen_be-careful-when-using-chatgpt-in-your-activity-7214519714465619969-35ot%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20LinkedIn%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20other%20employers%20reported%20seeing%20a%20similar%20trend%20of%20a%20spike%20in%20AI-written%20job%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChristina%20Hallman%2C%20who%20is%20head%20of%20demand%20generation%20for%20cybersecurity%20risk%20management%20company%20Outpost24%2C%20recently%20said%20she%20received%20over%20250%20applications%20for%20two%20open%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20Insider%20she%20estimated%20that%2045%25%20of%20the%20optional%20cover%20letters%20were%20AI-generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20over%20to%20ChatGPT%20and%20I%20put%20in%20our%20live%20job%20posting%2C%20and%20I%20said%20give%20me%20a%20cover%20letter%2C%26quot%3B%20Hallman%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20spit%20out%20almost%20the%20identical%20template%20that%20I%20was%20receiving%20time%20and%20time%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20it%20didn't%20necessarily%20eliminate%20the%20candidate%20from%20the%20running%2C%20but%20when%20it%20came%20down%20to%20choosing%20between%20an%20application%20that%20used%20a%20ChatGPT-generated%20cover%20letter%20and%20a%20similar%20one%20that%20didn't%2C%20the%20latter%20would%20be%20hired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20just%20ended%20being%20like%2C%20well%2C%20it's%20not%20helping%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20better%20to%20have%20just%20not%20attached%20anything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHallman%2C%20who%20said%20she%20has%20a%20decade%20of%20hiring%20experience%2C%20said%20that%20she's%20seen%20a%20noticeable%20increase%20in%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20in%20applicants%20over%20the%20past%20one%20to%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20likely%20going%20to%20keep%20climbing%20as%20ChatGPT%20and%20other%20AI%20tools%20become%20more%20accessible%20%E2%80%94%20and%20popular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icims.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2FClassOfReport_2023.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2023%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20conducted%20by%20iCIMS%20found%20that%2047%25%20of%20college%20seniors%20were%20interested%20in%20using%20ChatGPT%20or%20other%20AI%20bots%20to%20write%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%20cover%20letters%2C%20while%2025%25%20of%20Gen%20Z%20who%20were%20surveyed%20said%20they%20already%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20recruiters%20have%20considered%20creating%20%26quot%3BAI-proof%26quot%3B%20questions%2C%20such%20as%20requiring%20an%20introductory%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-got-my-first-million-users-loom-vinay-hiremath-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELoom%3C%2Fa%3E%20video.%20Others%20have%20even%20set%20chatbot%20traps%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fkarinemellata%2Fstatus%2F1805429294841446815%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esneaking%20hidden%20instructions%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20LLMs%20that%20show%20up%20in%20the%20applicant's%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Knutzen%20said%20his%20company%20did%20contemplate%20using%20videos%20or%20other%20questions%20that%20could%20cut%20down%20on%20the%20likelihood%20of%20AI-generated%20responses%2C%20they%20decided%20against%20it%20due%20to%20concerns%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bbarrier%20for%20entry%20would%20be%20too%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20comments%20under%20Knutzen's%20post%20said%20that%20job%20seekers%20were%20simply%20leveling%20the%20playing%20field%20with%20recruiters%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-more-worried-finding-job-laid-off-unemployed-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincreasingly%2