anned-wedding-never-happened-not-doing-it-again-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Retest%2C%20Haryana%20NEET%20Centre%20With%20Most%20Top%20Scorers%20Gave%20This%20Result...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20NEET%20testing%20centre%20in%20Haryana%2C%20which%20had%20six%20students%20scoring%20a%20perfect%20720%20out%20of%20720%20marks%2C%20now%20shows%20a%20stark%20contrast%20with%20no%20one%20scoring%20above%20682%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court-mandated%20retest%20on%20June%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20analysis%20of%20NEET%20data%20revealed%20that%20Hardayal%20Public%20School%20in%20Haryana's%20Bahadurgarh%20had%20a%20total%20of%20494%20students%20appearing%20for%20the%20re-examination.%20Among%20them%2C%20the%20highest%20score%20was%20682%2C%20achieved%20by%20only%20one%20student.%20Additionally%2C%20only%2013%20students%20managed%20to%20score%20above%20600%20marks%2C%20a%20significant%20drop%20from%20the%20results%20of%20the%20May%205%20exam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20surrounding%20the%20centre%20began%20when%20the%20NEET%20exam%20data%20was%20uploaded%2C%20showing%20six%20students%20with%20perfect%20scores.%20The%20improbability%20of%20such%20a%20feat%20led%20to%20widespread%20suspicion%20and%20uproar.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20intervened%2C%20cancelling%20the%20grace%20marks%20that%20had%20been%20awarded%20and%20ordering%201%2C563%20candidates%20to%20retake%20the%20exam.%20Of%20these%2C%20about%20800%20students%20appeared%20for%20the%20re-examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20last%20original%20NEET-UG%20examination%2C%20over%20500%20students%20sat%20for%20the%20exam%20at%20the%20centre.%20Additionally%2C%20two%20candidates%20scored%20718%20and%20719%20marks%20respectively.%20These%20results%20were%20deemed%20mathematically%20improbable%2C%20prompting%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20order%20a%20re-examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%20announced%20the%20centre%20and%20city-wise%20results%20for%20the%20medical%20entrance%20exam%20NEET-UG%2C%20following%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order.%20The%20results%2C%20initially%20declared%20on%20June%205%2C%20were%20re-published%20to%20mask%20the%20identities%20of%20the%20aspirants.%20This%20measure%20aimed%20to%20determine%20whether%20candidates%20from%20allegedly%20tainted%20centres%20scored%20disproportionately%20high%20marks%20compared%20to%20those%20from%20other%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEET-UG%20exam%2C%20held%20on%20May%205%2C%20took%20place%20across%204%2C750%20centres%20in%20571%20cities%2C%20including%2014%20international%20locations%2C%20accommodating%20over%2024%20lakh%20candidates.%20Allegations%20of%20irregularities%2C%20including%20a%20paper%20leak%2C%20have%20put%20the%20exam%20under%20intense%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20set%20to%20resume%20hearings%20on%20the%20matter%20on%20July%2022%2C%20addressing%20multiple%20petitions%20seeking%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20exam%2C%20a%20re-test%2C%20and%20a%20court-monitored%20probe%20into%20the%20allegations%20of%20malpractice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721472600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fm6tes5mg_neet-protest_625x300_24_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-results-neet-ug-after-retest-haryana-neet-centre-with-most-top-scorers-gave-this-result-6147854%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20NEET%20testing%20centre%20in%20Haryana%2C%20which%20had%20six%20students%20scoring%20a%20perfect%20720%20out%20of%20720%20marks%2C%20now%20shows%20a%20stark%20contrast%20with%20no%20one%20scoring%20above%20682%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court-mandated%20retest%20on%20June%2024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-results-neet-ug-after-retest-haryana-neet-centre-with-most-top-scorers-gave-this-result-6147854%22%2C%22