.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20places%20like%20Kurukshetra%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Haridwar%20in%20Uttarakhand%20have%20also%20placed%20restrictions%20on%20non-vegetarian%20restaurants%20and%20the%20open%20sale%20of%20meat%2C%20fish%20and%20eggs%2C%20it%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThese%20bans%20disproportionately%20impact%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20which%20supplies%20meat%20and%20poultry%2C%20and%20the%20majority%20population%2C%20which%20consumes%20non-vegetarian%20food.%20It%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20Jains%20abstain%20from%20onions%2C%20potatoes%2C%20and%20all%20root%20vegetables%2C%20while%20Muslims%20do%20not%20eat%20pork...%20Food%20is%20inherently%20a%20personal%20choice%2C%20and%20imposing%20one's%20dietary%20preferences%20on%20others%20is%20fundamentally%20unfair.%20Everyone%20should%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20choose%20their%20food.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20political%20high-handedness%20disregards%20the%20dietary%20practices%20of%20a%20vast%20majority%20of%20people%2C%20including%20Muslims%2C%20Christians%2C%20scheduled%20castes%2C%20scheduled%20tribes%2C%20and%20OBCs%2C%20who%2C%20generally%20speaking%2C%20consume%20non-vegetarian%20food.%20Many%20upper-caste%20communities%20like%20Bhumihars%20and%20Rajputs%20include%20non-vegetarian%20items%20in%20their%20daily%20diet%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20editorial%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20newspaper%20of%20explicitly%20targeting%20Jain%20culture%20and%20one%20its%20holiest%20pilgrimage%20centres%2C%20Mr%20Siroya%2C%20who%20is%20an%20MP%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20said%20the%20Muslim%20community%20has%20%26quot%3Bgreatly%20respected%26quot%3B%20Jain%20saints%20and%20sentiments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20lived%20in%20harmony.%20A%20newspaper%20should%20not%20attempt%20to%20create%20discord%20between%20the%20two%20communities%20to%20prove%20its%20misplaced%20liberalism.%20Again%2C%20Palitana%20is%20a%20small%20town%20and%20not%20a%20city%20