%20advice%20and%20examine%20candidates'%20policies%20and%20records.%20This%20election%2C%20though%2C%20I'm%20also%20considering%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20spent%20nearly%20all%20of%20my%2082%20years%20in%20Michigan.%20I've%20seen%20the%20state%20change%20politically%2C%20watching%20it%20go%20from%20blue%20to%20red%20as%20I%20went%20from%20childhood%2C%20to%20adulthood%2C%20to%20old%20age.%20And%20though%20I'm%20as%20engaged%20as%20ever%2C%20reading%20the%20newspaper%20far%20more%20than%20other%20residents%20at%20my%20retirement%20home%2C%20I%20know%20that%20an%20octogenarian%20is%20generally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-americans-embarrassed-by-trump-and-biden-poll-pew-research-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20up%20for%20the%20job%20of%20president%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%2C%20for%20one%2C%20cannot%20imagine%20being%20the%20country's%20Commander%20in%20Chief.%20The%20job%20demands%20that%20you're%20constantly%20alert%20and%20up-to-date%2C%20moving%20at%20a%20clip%20that's%20difficult%20even%20for%20a%20young%20person%20to%20maintain.%20There%20are%20some%20days%20where%20I%20can't%20even%20read%20past%20a%20certain%20time%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20hot%20it%20is%20or%20how%20busy%20I've%20been.%20Being%20the%20president%2C%20you%20can't%20count%20on%20a%20full%20eight%20or%20nine%20hours%20of%20rest%20each%20night.%20What%20if%20someone%20attacks%20American%20ships%2C%20or%20there%20are%20urgent%20updates%20abroad%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20may%20be%20well-informed%20about%20the%20issues%2C%20but%20he%20doesn't%20seem%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjoe-biden-refers-kamala-harris-vice-president-trump-nato-conference-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equick%20in%20interviews%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20on%20his%20feet.%20We're%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjoe-biden-doctor-parkinsons-expert-visits-routine-neurology-clinics-2024-7%5C%22%20