com%2F82-year-old-michigan-voter-biden-and-trump-too-old-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arbaaz-Sshura%20snapped%20in%20the%20city%3A%20video%20inside%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721471508000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111884389%2Cimgsize-318946.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Farbaaz-khan-and-wife-sshura-snapped-in-the-city-video-inside%2Farticleshow%2F111884406.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111884406.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERecently%2C%20Ridhima%20Pandit%2C%20who%20is%20a%20popular%20television%20actress%20known%20for%20her%20role%20in%20%E2%80%98Bahu%20Hamari%20Rajnikant%E2%80%99%2C%20opened%20up%20about%20her%20close%20bond%20with%20Sshura%20Khan.%20She%20was%20also%20all%20praises%20for%20Arbaaz%20Khan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Farbaaz-khan-and-wife-sshura-snapped-in-the-city-video-inside%2Farticleshow%2F111884406.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Recovery%20Of%20Austrian%20Gun%20'Steyr%20AUG'%20From%20J%26amp%3BK%20Terrorists%20Means%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20recovery%20of%20an%20Austrian%20assault%20rifle%20from%20two%20slain%20foreign%20terrorists%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Keran%20sector%20on%20July%2018%20has%20added%20another%20complex%20dimension%20to%20the%20ongoing%20terrorism%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20weapon%20to%20be%20recovered%20from%20the%20terrorists%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20on%20September%2012%2C%201988.%20Terrorists%20had%20attacked%20the%20house%20of%20the%20then%20Deputy%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Police%20(DIG)%20Ali%20Mohammad%20Watali%2C%20in%20Raj%20Bagh%20residential%20area%20of%20Srinagar%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20terrorist%20identified%20as%20Aijaz%20Dar%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20the%20nearby%20Jawahar%20Nagar%20area%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20retaliatory%20firing%20by%20the%20guards%20at%20the%20DIG's%20house%20and%20one%20assault%20rifle%20was%20recovered%20from%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20senior%20police%20officer%2C%20Shaikh%20Owais%2C%20was%20the%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(SP)%2C%20Srinagar%20at%20that%20time.%20Owais%20was%20among%20the%20first%20senior%20officers%20to%20reach%20the%20DIG's%20residence%20since%20he%20also%20lived%20in%20the%20same%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20weapon%20not%20in%20use%20in%20the%20police%20force%2C%20nor%20was%20it%20the%20standard%20weapon%20issued%20to%20the%20army%20back%20then.%20At%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20experts%20called%20in%20from%20the%20army%2C%20the%20weapon%20was%20identified%20as%20a%20Kalashnikov.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20belonged%20to%20a%20family%20of%20assault%20rifles%20also%20known%20as%20AK%20platform%2C%20AK%20rifle%20or%20simply%20AK%20based%20on%20the%20original%20design%20of%20Mikhail%20Kalashnikov.%20Experts%20identified%20the%20rifle%20as%20AK-47%2C%20officially%20known%20as%20the%20Avtomat%20Kalashnikova%20which%20is%20the%20originating%20firearm%20of%20the%20Kalashnikov%20family%20of%20rifles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20developed%20in%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20by%20Russian%20small-arms%20designer%20Mikhail%20Kalashnikov%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%2020th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAK-47's%20name%20stands%20for%20Automat%20Kalashnikova%201947%2C%20the%20year%20it%20was%20first%20produced.%20In%201949%2C%20the%20AK-47%20became%20the%20assault%20rifle%20of%20the%20Soviet%20Army%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20since%201988%2C%20the%20terrorists%20started%20using%20long-range%20sniper%20rifles%20and%20also%20the%20subsequent%20versions%20of%20the%20AK%20rifle%20series%20like%20AK-54%20and%20AK-74%20denoting%20the%20year%20of%20manufacture%20of%20the%20rifle%20with%20improvements%20over%20the%20original%20AK-47%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20police%20force%20was%20not%20issued%20any%20assault%20rifle%20of%20the%20AK%20series%20till%20then%2C%20and%20to%20combat%20the%20firepower%20of%20the%20adversary%2C%20police%2C%20paramilitary%20and%20the%20army%20were%20subsequently%20issued%20assault%20rifles%20of%20the%20AK%20series%20as%20well%20in%20addition%20to%20Indian-made%20INSAS%20rifles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20possession%20of%20AK%20assault%20rifles%20by%20the%20terrorists%20unequivocally%20established%20that%20they%20had%20been%20trained%20and%20issued%20weapons%20by%20trainers%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20army.%20Due%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20Russians%20in%20Afghanistan%20and%20Pakistan's%20support%20to%20the%20Afghan%20militias%2C%20AK%20rifles%20were%20aplenty%20in%20Pakistan%20since%20practically%20no%20border%20existed%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20at%20that%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20senior%20intelligence%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20terrorism%20intensified%20due%20to%20the%20entry%20of%20foreign%20mercenaries%20into%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20by%20the%20middle%20of%201990s%2C%20more%20weapons%20in%20their%20improvised%20versions%20like%20AK-54%2C%20AK-74%20and%20under-barrel%20grenade%20launchers%20(UBGLs)%20came%20to%20be%20used%20by%20the%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20foreign%20mercenaries%20were%20battle-hardened%2C%20the%20security%20forces%20had%20to%20live%20up%20to%20the%20growing%20challenge%20by%20introducing%20the%20Para%20commandos%20and%20those%20trained%20in%20mountain%20warfare%20into%20its%20anti-terrorism%20operations%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJ%26amp%3BK%20police%20also%20underwent%20a%20sweeping%20change%20in%20its%20training%20of%20commandos%2C%20use%20and%20expertise%20of%20modern%20assault%20rifles%20and%20strenuous%20training%20in%20developing%20stamina%20and%20focus.%20Commitment%20to%20eradicate%20terrorism%20and%20usher%20in%20peace%20was%20the%20preamble%20of%20such%20training%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20supervising%20physical%20and%20weapon%20handling%20training%20of%20the%20local%20police%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParamilitary%20forces%20like%20BSF%20and%20CRPF%20were%20not%20behind%20in%20bringing%20their%20troops%20up%20to%20the%20maximum%20level%20of%20efficiency%20to%20deal%20with%20terrorism%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20terrorism%20started%20getting%20more%20hands%20by%20way%20of%20foreign%20mercenaries%20who%20were%20pushed%20into%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20from%20across%20the%20border%2C%20motivated%20and%20indoctrinated%20by%20both%20religious%20fanaticism%20and%20the%20lure%20of%20money%2C%20the%20handlers%20and%20their%20masters%20in%20the%20Pakistan%20army%20started%20encouraging%20them%20with%20better%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2011%2C%202022%2C%20one%20M4%20carbine%20rifle%20was%20recovered%20from%20an%20encounter%20site%20in%20the%20Awantipora%20area%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Pulwama%20district%20where%20Jaish-e-Muhammad%20commander%2C%20Kaiser%20Koka%20and%20another%20terrorist%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20new%20challenge%20for%20the%20security%20forces.%20The%20M4%20carbine%20also%20replaced%20most%20submachine%20guns%20and%20selected%20handguns%20in%20US%20military%20service%2C%20as%20it%20fired%20more%20effective%20rifle%20ammunition%20that%20offered%20superior%20stopping%20power%20and%20was%20better%20able%20to%20penetrate%20modern%20body%20armour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20review%20had%20become%20necessary%20of%20the%20bulletproof%20vests%20issued%20to%20the%20security%20forces.%20The%20older%20version%20of%20the%20bullet%20proof%20jacket%20wouldn't%20suffice%20to%20meet%20the%20new%20challenge.%20Better%20and%20lighter%20BP%20jackets%20have%20been%20issued%20to%20security%20forces%20fighting%20terrorism%20and%20these%20are%20designed%20to%20stop%20the%20armour-piercing%20bullets%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another%20senior%20police%20officer%20deployed%20on%20anti-terrorism%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20M4%20assault%20rifle%20is%20US-made%20and%20it%20is%20issued%20to%20the%20American%20army%2C%20it%20is%20obvious%20that%20while%20leaving%20Afghanistan%2C%20the%20US%20forces%20left%20behind%20some%20of%20their%20sophisticated%20weaponry%20which%20came%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Afghan%20fighters.%20This%20assault%20rifle%20found%20its%20way%20into%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20through%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2017%2C%202024%2C%20two%20foreign%20terrorists%20were%20killed%20by%20the%20army%20while%20foiling%20an%20infiltration%20bid%20on%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20in%20the%20Keran%20sector.%20A%20Steyr%20AUG%20assault%20rifle%20was%20recovered%20from%20the%20slain%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20StG%2077%20(Sturmgewehr%2077)%20is%20the%20designation%20given%20by%20the%20Austrian%20Armed%20Forces%20when%20they%20adopted%20the%20Steyr%20AUG%20in%201977.%20This%20is%20the%20standard%20assault%20rifle%20issued%20to%20the%20Austrian%20army.%20The%20Steyr%20bullpup%20assault%20rifle%20is%20only%20matched%20by%20the%20Israeli-made%20Tavor%20assault%20rifle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETavor%20is%20a%20gas-operated%2C%20selective-fire%20bullpup%20assault%20rifle%20built%20around%20a%20long-stroke%20piston%20system.%20The%20main%20objective%20behind%20the%20development%20of%20Tavor%20is%20to%20maximise%20reliability%2C%20durability%2C%20simplicity%20of%20design%2C%20and%20maintenance-free%2C%20particularly%20under%20unfavourable%20or%20battlefield%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTavor%20has%20a%20semi-automatic%20mode%2C%20burst%20mode%20and%20full-auto%20mode%20chambered%20in%20standard%205.56x45%20mm%20ammunition.%20It%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20more%20reliable%20and%20accurate%20than%20the%20M4%20carbine%20of%20the%20US%20and%20Steyr%20of%20Austria.%20The%20Tavor%20TAR-21%20holds%20magazines%20of%2030%20rounds%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20arms%20expert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20challenges%20are%20in%20plenty%20for%20the%20security%20forces%20fighting%20terrorism%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20weapons%20systems%2C%20armour-resistant%20apparel%20and%20other%20equipment%20used%20by%20our%20security%20forces%20are%20regularly%20and%20constantly%20reviewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20couple%20of%20M4%20carbine%20rifles%20or%20Austrian%20bullpup%20assault%20rifles%20cannot%20save%20the%20terrorist%20from%20a%20professionally%20trained%20and%20highly%20modernised%20army%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20senior%20intelligence%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721471460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fvn25in6g_steyr_625x300_20_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-recovery-of-austrian-assault-rifle-from-j-k-terrorists-means-6146713%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20recovery%20of%20an%20Austrian%20assault%20rifle%20from%20two%20slain%20foreign%20terrorists%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Keran%20sector%20on%20July%2018%20has%20added%20another%20complex%20dimension%20to%20the%20ongoing%20terrorism%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-recovery-of-austrian-assault-rifle-from-j-k-terrorists-means-6146713%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-recovery-of-austrian-assault-rifle-from-j-k-terrorists-means-6146713%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nd