tioning.%20The%20rucker%20wasn't%20particularly%20comfortable%2C%20especially%20as%20I%20got%20sweatier%20and%20sweatier.%20And%20boy%2C%20did%20I%20get%20sweaty.%20I%20wasn't%20expecting%20to%20need%20a%20shower%20afterward%2C%20but%20I%20definitely%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoosening%20the%20straps%20meant%20my%20back%20could%20breathe%20somewhat%20(I%20didn't%20love%20the%20feeling%20of%20my%20sweaty%20back%20on%20the%20rucker)%2C%20but%20it%20also%20meant%20the%20weight%20moved%20around%20and%20hit%20my%20back%20with%20every%20step%2C%20which%20wasn't%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20each%20ruck%20I've%20done%2C%20I've%20swiftly%20felt%20my%20heart%20rate%20increase%20to%20what%20felt%20like%20higher%20than%20during%20a%20normal%20walk%2C%20so%20I%20could%20tell%20my%20body%20was%20working%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%2020%20minutes%20or%20so%2C%20I%20could%20feel%20my%20upper%20body%20and%20shoulders%20fatiguing.%20After%20half%20an%20hour%20or%20so%2C%20I%20feel%20myself%20starting%20to%20tire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERucking%2C%20I%20have%20learned%2C%20doesn't%20help%20you%20relax%20and%20decompress%20like%20a%20walk%20might.%20It's%20a%20workout.%20And%20one%20I%20should%20not%20attempt%20immediately%20after%20eating%20my%20lunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20learned%20that%20the%20ruck%20isn't%20something%20I%20will%20just%20always%20throw%20on%20when%20going%20for%20my%20daily%20walk.%20When%20I%20want%20to%20get%20a%20full%20body%20workout%20in%20while%20enjoying%20the%20outdoors%2C%20I%20will%20ruck%2C%20when%20I%20need%20to%20decompress%2C%20I%20will%20walk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a0bdfb1d-931d-4b0f-af20-553648a4751d%5C%22%3EThe%20ruck%20is%20useful%20for%20workouts%20too%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20weekday%20evening%20I%20told%20myself%20I'd%20go%20for%20a%20ruck%2C%20but%20what%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20do%20was%20watch%20Wimbledon.%20So%20I%20decided%20I'd%20get%20the%20best%20of%20both%20worlds%20and%20exercise%20in%20front%20of%20the%20television%20while%20wearing%20the%20rucker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20ended%20up%20being%20a%20great%20workout%2C%20and%20definitely%20left%20me%20with%20aching%20muscles%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20movements%20including%20lunges%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsquats-best-exercise-building-muscle-powerlifter-blaine-sumner-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esquats%2C%20and%20Bulgarian%20split%20squats%3C%2Fa%3E%20all%20while%20wearing%20the%20rucker%2C%20and%20it%20really%20leveled%20up%20what%20would%20have%20otherwise%20been%20an%20easy%20bodyweight%20workout%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ruck%20also%20has%20handles%20both%20at%20the%20top%20and%20the%20bottom%2C%20meaning%20you%20can%20easily%20hold%20it%20in%20your%20hands%20for%20different%20types%20of%20exercises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20will%20definitely%20keep%20using%20the%20rucker%2C%20both%20on%20walks%20and%20for%20home%20workouts.%20If%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20invest%20in%20much%20fitness%20equipment%2C%20a%20rucker%20is%20a%20really%20versatile%20piece%20of%20kit%20that%20can%20tick%20a%20lot%20of%20boxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20make%20sure%20you%20factor%20in%20time%20to%20shower%20after%20using%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frucking-buzzy-workout-busy-fit-efficient-daily-walk-challenging-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721471283000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66992d6d49138fa6f6e36d1c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frucking-buzzy-workout-busy-fit-efficient-daily-walk-challenging-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Health%20and%20fitness%20reporter%20Rachel%20Hosie%20has%20been%20strength%20training%20for%20years%20and%20goes%20on%20daily%20walks%2C%20but%20she%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20challenging%20rucking%20was.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rhosi