067%20lakh%20and%20filed%20a%20complaint.%20Odisha's%20Rourkela%20Police%20busted%20a%20cyber-crime%20syndicate%20on%20December%2030%20and%20arrested%20eight%20people%20allegedly%20involved%20in%20moving%20people%20to%20Cambodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20also%20issued%20an%20advisory%20for%20those%20travelling%20to%20Cambodia%20for%20jobs.%20It%20asked%20Indian%20nationals%20to%20secure%20employment%20only%20through%20authorized%20agents%20approved%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20embassy%20noted%20that%20these%20fake%20jobs%20are%20for%20posts%20like%20'Digital%20Sales%20and%20Marketing%20Executives'%20or%20'Customer%20Support%20Service'%20by%20dubious%20companies%20involved%20in%20call-centre%20scams%20and%20crypto-currency%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721467500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fkqo7vqk_cambodia_625x300_20_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F14-indians-rescued-from-cyber-slavery-in-cambodia-wait-to-return-home-6147228%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2214%20Indians%2C%20fraudulently%20taken%20to%20Cambodia%20and%20forced%20into%20cyber%20fraud%20by%20trafficking%20rackets%2C%20have%20appealed%20to%20the%20Indian%20embassy%20to%20facilitate%20their%20return%20to%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F14-indians-rescued-from-cyber-slavery-in-cambodia-wait-to-return-home-6147228%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F14-indians-rescued-from-cyber-slavery-in-cambodia-wait-to-return-home-6147228%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F14-indians-rescued-from-cyber-slavery-in-cambodia-wait-to-return-home-6147228%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A