tps%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsri-lanka-vs-india-2024%2Ft-dilip-retained-two-huge-additions-in-gautam-gambhirs-team-india-staff-reports-big-claim-6147238%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsri-lanka-vs-india-2024%2Ft-dilip-retained-two-huge-additions-in-gautam-gambhirs-team-india-staff-reports-big-claim-6147238%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Panel%20Of%20IAS%20Officers%20To%20Tackle%20Stray%20Dog%20Menace%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20appointed%20seven%20senior%20IAS%20officers%20to%20manage%20the%20escalating%20stray%20dog%20menace%20across%20the%20state.%20The%20stray%20dog%20crisis%20has%20become%20a%20significant%20concern%2C%20not%20only%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20in%20residential%20areas%20but%20also%20within%20government%20premises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20General%20Administration%20Department%20has%20issued%20an%20order%20forming%20a%20committee%20of%2015%20members%2C%20including%20IAS%20officers%20up%20to%20the%20level%20of%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2021%2C000%20dog%20bite%20cases%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20annually.%20In%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20stray%20dogs%20have%20killed%20five%20people%20including%20those%20who%20died%20from%20rabies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bhopal%20alone%2C%20hospitals%20receive%20an%20average%20of%2055%20cases%20of%20dog%20bites%20daily.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%201%2C%20Kunal%20from%20Lalghati%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20was%20mauled%20by%20a%20dog%2C%20requiring%20eight%20stitches.%20Five%20days%20later%2C%2016-year-old%20Ravi%20Sahu%20was%20attacked%20by%20stray%20dogs%20while%20visiting%20a%20shrine%20in%20Raisen%20with%20his%20family.%20On%20July%209%2C%20a%20man%20in%20Sethani%20Ghat%2C%20Hoshangabad%20was%20attacked%20by%20stray%20dogs%2C%20resulting%20in%20deep%20wounds%20on%20his%20leg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20government%20says%20the%20decision%20was%20driven%20by%20alarming%20data%2C%20the%20opposition%20claims%20it%20highlights%20governmental%20failures.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20taken%20this%20decision%20after%20thoroughly%20examining%20our%20data.%20Our%20priority%20is%20to%20save%20lives%2C%20which%20is%20why%20we%20have%20formed%20this%20committee%20of%20officers%2C%26quot%3B%20Animal%20husbandry%20minister%20Lakhan%20Patel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20situation%20on%20ground%20is%20dire.%20While%20the%20Bhopal%20Municipal%20Corporation's%20shelter%20home%20is%20overcrowded%20with%20stray%20dogs%2C%20dozens%20of%20people%20queue%20up%20every%20day%20in%20hospitals%20to%20get%20rabies%20injections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHospital%20data%20reveals%20alarming%20figures.%20In%202022%2C%20over%208%2C124%20dog%20bite%20incidents%20were%20recorded%20and%20in%202023%2C%20the%20number%20almost%20doubled%20to%2016%2C387.%20%C2%A0In%20the%20first%20five%20months%20of%202024%2C%20as%20many%20as%207%2C728%20cases%20of%20dog%20bites%20have%20been%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20organisations%20working%20for%20animal%20welfare%20have%20welcomed%20the%20decision.%20%26quot%3BThis%20government%20step%20is%20commendable.%20These%20senior%20officials%20will%20make%20good%20decisions%20and%20solve%20the%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20Swati%20Gaurav%2C%20President%2C%20People%20for%20Animals%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721467020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-05%2Fstray-dogs-generic_650x400_71525256961.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-madhya-pradesh-panel-of-ias-officers-to-tackle-stray-dog-menace-6147302%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20appointed%20seven%20senior%20IAS%20officers%20to%20manage%20the%20escalating%20stray%20dog%20menace%20across%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%2