s%20already%20evaluating%20470%20proposals%20on%20'Accelerated%20research%20on%206G%20Ecosystem'.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721457900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F1kfevmfo_6g-network-6g-mobile-network-generic-ians_625x300_20_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-play-crucial-role-in-shaping-infra-for-6g-networks-worldwide-6145843%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Centre%20will%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20shaping%20standards%20and%20infrastructure%20for%206G%20networks%20worldwide%2C%20Dr%20Neeraj%20Mittal%2C%20Secretary%20(Telecom)%2C%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-play-crucial-role-in-shaping-infra-for-6g-networks-worldwide-6145843%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-play-crucial-role-in-shaping-infra-for-6g-networks-worldwide-6145843%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-play-crucial-role-in-shaping-infra-for-6g-networks-worldwide-6145843%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NEET-UG%20Centre-Wise%20Results%20Declared%20Ahead%20Of%20Supreme%20Court%20Deadline%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENational%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%20has%20announced%20the%20results%20of%20the%20National%20Eligibility%20cum%20Entrance%20Test-%20Undergraduate%20(NEET-%20UG)%202024%20for%20all%20the%20students%2C%20city%20and%20centre-wise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECandidates%20who%20appeared%20in%20the%20exam%20can%20check%20their%20results%20on%20the%20official%20website%20of%20NTA%20NEET%20at%20exams.nta.ac.in%2FNEET%2F%20and%20also%20on%20neet.ntaonline.in.%C2%A0%3