nicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357678%2Fsustainable-architecture-titan-integrity-tata-bengaluru-office-surrounded-by-lake-trees-plants-mindspace-architects%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Looking%20for%20a%20Lawyer%3F%20Startup%20Helps%20Resolve%20Disputes%20Outside%20Courts%2C%20Solved%2035%20Lakh%20Cases%20Online%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20B2C%20company%20had%20been%20providing%20software%20solutions%20to%20other%20startups%20in%20their%20day-to-day%20operations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20in%20question%20operated%20on%20a%20paid%20subscription%20model.%20However%2C%20it%20did%20not%20receive%20timely%20payments%20for%20their%20services.%20It%20had%20become%20a%20task%20to%20recover%20the%20invoices%20from%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20raise%20invoices%20but%20did%20not%20get%20paid%20in%20time.%20As%20a%20result%20of%20this%2C%20we%20were%20forced%20to%20disconnect%20their%20services%20until%20they%20paid%20but%20keeping%20a%20track%20was%20getting%20difficult.%20There%20were%20invoices%20amounting%20to%20lakhs%20of%20rupees%20which%20were%20stuck%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20one%20of%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20employees%20on%20a%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20tried%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20customers%20through%20multiple%20phone%20calls%20and%20emails%2C%20but%20received%20no%20response.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20have%20the%20bandwidth%20to%20file%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F265312%2Fjai-bhim-real-life-suriya-amazon-prime-justice-chandru-madras-high-court-judge%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecourt%20case%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20physically%20visit%20the%20court.%20So%2C%20we%20sought%20help%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F