%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evisited%20his%20family%20farm%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20two%20days%2C%20he%20would%20live%20amidst%20nature%2C%20with%20no%20contact%20of%20any%20sort%20with%20the%20outside%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20light%20at%20night%2C%20no%20air%20conditioning%2C%20no%20laptops%20and%20no%20network%20for%20these%20two%20days.%20He%20would%20start%20his%20day%20by%20visiting%20the%20farms%20and%20getting%20his%20hands%20dirty.%20This%20routine%20continued%20for%20almost%20three%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20fine%20day%2C%20a%20label%20startled%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20pesticides%20that%20we%20were%20using%20had%20the%20word%20poison%20written%20on%20them%20in%20three%20languages.%20What%20were%20we%20growing%3F%E2%80%9D%20wonders%20Deepak%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20realisation%20that%20they%20were%20feeding%20poison%20to%20the%20soil%20and%20plants%2C%20and%20further%20consuming%20and%20selling%20this%20was%20a%20hard%20pill%20to%20swallow%20for%20this%20MBA%20graduate%20with%20a%20high-flying%20corporate%20career.%20As%20he%20studied%20ways%20to%20start%20organic%20farming%2C%20he%20was%20hit%20by%20another%20blow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20mother%20had%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20808px)%20100vw%2C%20808px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-08-at-14.20.28-min-1721051668.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22808%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Deepak%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20spread%20organic%20farming%20across%20the%20country.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-08-at-14.20.28-min-1721051668.jpeg%20808w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-08-at-14.20.28-min-1721051668-189x300.jpeg%20189w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-08-at-14.20.28-min-1721051668-500x792.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-08-at-14.20.28-min-1721051668-768x1217.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-08-at-14.20.28-min-1721051668-150x238.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356972%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDeepak%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20spread%20organic%20farming%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20moment%20of%20truth%20for%20the%2048-year-old.%20From%20here%20on%2C%20all%20his%20efforts%20were%20directed%20towards%20moving%20to%20organic%20farming%20on%20their%2021-acre%20land.%20Wanting%20to%20spread%20the%20fruits%20of%20this%20natural%20labour%2C%20he%20started%20selling%20this%20produce%20in%20Delhi-NCR%3Cstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20mission%20to%20provide%20organic%20food%20to%20consumers%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354716%2Fvegetable-farmer-smarika-chandrakar-grows-tomatoes-cucumbers-brinjals-in-chhattisgarh-farming-mba-grad-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emotivate%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20shift%20to%20organic%20farming%2C%20he%20started%20Earthy%20Tales%20in%202017.%20Today%2C%20they%20work%20with%20over%20500%20farmers%20across%20the%20country%20and%20have%20served%2015%2C000%20consumers%2C%20making%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%204%20crore%20in%20FY%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20weekend%20visit%20that%20sparked%20an%20idea%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepak%20earlier%